# Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# Do NOT commit .env.local (it is already in .gitignore).
#
# VibePrompter is a Tauri desktop app. Most configuration lives in the
# app's settings UI (stored in SQLite + OS keyring), not here. These
# variables are only needed for development or custom builds.

# Override the Vite dev server port (default: 3000, set in vite.config.ts).
# VITE_DEV_PORT=3000

# Set to "true" to enable verbose frontend logging in development builds.
# VITE_DEBUG=false
